translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 命が無事に済む保証などはない。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There is no guarantee that life will be spared.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 幸運にも命までは失わずに済んでも、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even if, by some luck, you manage not to lose your life,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 敵の捕虜となる以上、最早マエリータ隊に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Once captured by the enemy, it will no longer be possible

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 合流することは不可能となるだろう。

ほんと、頼りになるよ、お前ら」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You guys really are someone I can rely on."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even if the opponent is a demon, I will defend this place to the death!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「彼らは戦いしかなかった我が人生において

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マエリータ隊がこっそりと

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: sneaked into the room believed to be where the Demon King was.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: よくもまあこんな騒ぎの中……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: How can he be asleep amidst such a commotion...?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 相手は魔王、どう誘拐するべきか悩みましたが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The opponent is the Demon King; we were wondering how to kidnap him...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: このまま運んでしまいましょう。マッスル」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's just carry him away like this, Muscle."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At the scholar's instruction, Muscle carried Miki.
Let's get out of here quickly!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ええ、このまま問題さえなければ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yes, as long as no problems arise...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 別れた皆も回収出来るかも知れません……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We might even be able to retrieve everyone we got separated from..."
